(2078, 'Grafana 中的 Data(IEC) 和 Data(metric)', '2078', 1549245240, 1578754550, '<!--markdown-->参见 https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mebibyte\r\n\r\nIEC 是以二进制来计算。\r\n\r\n```\r\n1 MiB = 2^20 bytes = 1024 kibibytes = 1048576 bytes\r\n\r\n1024 MiB = 1 gibibyte (GiB)\r\n```\r\n\r\nMetric 是以十进制计算。\r\n', 0, 1, NULL, 'post', 'publish', NULL, 1, '1', '1', '1', 0, 0, 'post', 0),
